{"tid":1997502,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"歐盟表態顯贊同調查武漢新冠病毒源頭並呼籲中国配合","createTime":"2020-05-01T16:50:16.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-02T04:13:05.000Z","uid":184679,"like":15,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"b280b7032f09015874fec63105c40b38a7d872d7","tid":1997502,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-01T16:50:16.000Z","msg":"隨着愈來愈多國家要求追查新冠肺炎病毒起源，歐盟執委會主席馮德萊恩（Ursula von der Leyen）接受美國CNBC電視台專訪時，也首度表態支持此一行動，認為將有助於改善預警系統，並呼籲中國配合調查。<br />\n<br />\n繼美國、澳大利亞、瑞典、德國和英國政府或國會，表明支持對新冠肺炎病毒展開獨立調查後，馮德萊恩星期四向CNBC表示，她希望中國與歐盟和其他國家合作，深入調查病毒如何產生，以建立能夠真正發揮作用的早期預警系統，為下次疫情來臨做好準備，據她指出，&ldquo;這對我們所有人都很重要，你永遠不知道下一個病毒何時開始。&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n歐盟執委會主席馮德萊恩也敦促各國必須從此次危機中汲取教訓，提高透明度。例如，歐盟應建立更健全的數據系統，來應對類似武漢肺炎的疾病流行，此次疫情結束後就應着手開始。至於是否擔心歐盟因此打壞與中國的關係，馮德萊恩直言不這麼認為，&ldquo;因為這關係到整體的利益&rdquo;。<br />\n<br />\n據該報道稱，歐盟近日飽受外界抨擊，被指屈服於中國壓力，軟化原本指控中國利用疫情散布假消息的報告。雖然歐盟官方駁斥相關控訴，但外交和安全政策高級代表波瑞爾（Josep Borrel）並未否認中國曾就此事提出關切。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.rfi.fr/tw/中國/20200501-歐盟表態顯贊同調查新冠病毒源頭並呼籲中國配合\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.rfi.fr%2Ftw%2F%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%2F20200501-%E6%AD%90%E7%9B%9F%E8%A1%A8%E6%85%8B%E9%A1%AF%E8%B4%8A%E5%90%8C%E8%AA%BF%E6%9F%A5%E6%96%B0%E5%86%A0%E7%97%85%E6%AF%92%E6%BA%90%E9%A0%AD%E4%B8%A6%E5%91%BC%E7%B1%B2%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%E9%85%8D%E5%90%88&d=29ui5Tvv6aczeWgqk0vw14429F%2FWQzM9xP7K%2BddLk1E%3D&h=c4794f21\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.rfi.fr/tw/中國/20200501-歐盟表態顯贊同調查新冠病毒源頭並呼籲中國配合</a>"},{"pid":"5143ad5297355a955b6709c7ac4e7296e231fded","tid":1997502,"uid":54373,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-01T16:52:04.000Z","msg":"班農話，歐美已重兵保護 P4實驗室變節共匪證人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8dc0bef76080bf8c031a0176a0d2c8e3323b6c87","tid":1997502,"uid":279311,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-01T16:53:04.000Z","msg":"歐盟都係睇定啲先<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b74c4f65f624e0ce5ad08b261211a50c76fc32a4","tid":1997502,"uid":31185,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-01T16:57:25.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"bac07f865234b434b9fd30d3f7fe3575e617da45","tid":1997502,"uid":104804,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-01T16:59:01.000Z","msg":"唔止查源頭<br />\n仲要查下中國有冇同世衛聯手隱瞞同專登散播疫情"},{"pid":"e1fb044b249db0bcf96d5fe5b74d6799ef1aff20","tid":1997502,"uid":182222,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-01T17:01:45.000Z","msg":"歐盟牆頭草黎<br />\n睇定D先咪炒車"},{"pid":"6ea8b4fc85e2cbaff3a3c1492e245f33a149c429","tid":1997502,"uid":249794,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-01T17:02:57.000Z","msg":"彈出彈入<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d8fd87d419762177e75c1e4135f8f0981c325184","tid":1997502,"uid":52658,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-01T17:03:13.000Z","msg":"兩家茶禮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"84e05c909054d61f2d38f18f24da260a0d990457","tid":1997502,"uid":5490,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d8fd87d419762177e75c1e4135f8f0981c325184","tid":1997502,"uid":52658,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-01T17:03:13.000Z","msg":"兩家茶禮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-01T17:12:12.000Z","msg":"賺人仔係會有錢，但大陸玩完，之後大家瓜分成個大陸原有既資產利益，條數一定大過睇大陸面色賺人仔好多既，無左大陸，大把野會去返歐洲個邊"},{"pid":"9a7c8f1041f6e8b4aa468b40c12f4789b9b2c9a0","tid":1997502,"uid":286309,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-01T18:07:25.000Z","msg":"支持呀 <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cc8bcf89e742efbfdd5906d222c41cf158baa4b2","tid":1997502,"uid":286309,"like":